Title : Giuseppe Moretti (botanist)
Text : '''Giuseppe Moretti''' (30 November 1782 in [[Roncaro]] – 1 December 1853) was an Italian [[botanist]].<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=BQ1KAAAAYAAJ&pg=PR30&lpg=PR30&dq=%22Giuseppe+Moretti%22+1782&source=bl&ots=xnFpGizvsK&sig=F89PqlZVH3Gs6h5hHweSBD9bRE0&hl=en&sa=X&ei=rEpbU-7SKam4yQGH6oDQCA&ved=0CEIQ6AEwBDgK#v=onepage&q=%22Giuseppe%20Moretti%22%201782&f=false Ampelografia: descrizione delle migliori varietà di viti per uve ..., Volume 1] by Girolamo Molon</ref>

He served as a professor of botany and as director of the botanical gardens at the [[University of Pavia]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://digitale.beic.it/primo_library/libweb/action/search.do?fn=search&ct=search&initialSearch=true&mode=Basic&tab=default_tab&indx=1&dum=true&srt=rank&vid=BEIC&frbg=&vl%28freeText0%29=%22Ex+libris+di+Giuseppe+Moretti%22&scp.scps=scope%3A%28RD01%29|title=Part of his library has been digitized and is available on the BEIC web site|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=}}</ref> (1826–1853). The genus ''[[Morettia]]'' (family [[Brassicaceae]]) was named in his honor by [[Augustin Pyramus de Candolle]].<ref>[https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/33355664 BHL] Taxonomic literature : a selective guide to botanical publications</ref>
[[File:Ex libris di Giuseppe Moretti, 87mm x 87mm, 1820.JPG|thumb|Giuseppe Moretti's ex libris]]

[[File:Ex libris di Giuseppe Moretti, 51mm x 50mm, 1810.jpg|thumb|Giuseppe Moretti's ex libris]]
== Published works ==
* ''Osservazioni sopra diverse specie di piante indigene dell'Italia'', 1818.
* ''Il botanico italiano, ossia, Discussioni sulla flora italica'', 1826.
* ''Prodromo di una monografia delle specie del genere Morus'', 1842
* ''Sugli Anacardi orientale e occidentale (Semecarpus anacardium, Linn. fil. et Anacardium occidentale, Linn.)'', 1851.<ref>[http://classify.oclc.org/classify2/ClassifyDemo?search-author-txt=%22Moretti%2C+Giuseppe%22 OCLC Classify] publications</ref>

